divs: Sighting Detailson may 8th. at 1:30 pm 13.3 miles into mt rainier state park in a road pull out we 6 - 8 people saw two disc shaped objects over a hilltop in mt rainier state park i was only able to take one picture before the two objects shot straight up threw the clouds and puff they were gone. i know these objects was not from this world and after that day it has changed our lives . i now beleave we are not alone. ufo northwest took my picture and ran it threw the mill found it to be a genien ufo they posted the picture on there web site so did coast to coast am . i hope ya'll can help me to understand maybe what is going on around here i looked into the recent history of reports from this area and there has been several reports with the same disc type objects in this area .
